Class ContainerTimestampWrapper

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class ContainerTimestampWrapper
extends Object

    An immutable wrapper that holds a CAdES timestamp and an optional ASiCArchiveManifest associated with it.
